      "rdf:value": "<L>6368<pc>0934<k1>Bikz<k2>Bikz\r\n{@√bhikṣ@}¦ (altes <ab>Desid.</ab> von bhaj), {%zu erlangen wünschen,%} daher 1〉 etwas [<ab>A.</ab> <ab>G.</ab>] {%erbitten;%} 2〉 etwas [<ab>A.</ab> <ab>G.</ab>] {%erwünschen,%} danach {%verlangen%} (von Göttern).\r\n<div n=\"H\">Stamm {@bhikṣa:@}\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-e [<per>1.</per> <ab>s.</ab> <ab>me.</ab>] 1〉 sumatím {171,1}; sukīrtím váruṇasya {219,1}.\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-ate 1〉 táva nā́ma {548,17} (avasyús).\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-anta [<ab>Co.</ab>] 1〉 rátnam {290,7}.\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-eta [<ab>Opt.</ab>] 1〉 sumnám {627,15}; {638,1}; pitvás {152,6}.\r\n<div n=\"H\"><ab>Part.</ab> {@bhíkṣamāṇa:@}\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-as 1〉 dráviṇam {295,6}. 2〉 amṛ́tasya cā́ruṇas {782,2} (<ls>SV.</ls> falsch bhákṣamāṇas).\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-ās [<ab>m.</ab>] 1〉 sumatím {73,7}; sumnám {522,6}; śrávasas {606,7}. — 2〉 stutím jaritúr {857,5}.\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-e [<ab>d.</ab> <ab>f.</ab>] 1〉 prasavám {267,2} (vípāṭ śutudrī́).\r\n<div n=\"TS\">-ās [<ab>N.</ab> <ab>p.</ab> <ab>f.</ab>] 1〉 sumatím {73,6} (síndhavas); dráviṇam {526,3} (matáyas); {337,9} (manīṣā́s).\r\n<LEND>"
